        "text_settings": "My Story",
        "caption_settings": "<p>At Avni Life, my mission is to empower women dealing with hormonal imbalances—just like I once did. My personal journey with PCOS brought challenges like hair loss and acne that deeply affected my confidence and spirit. I knew there had to be a better way to tackle these issues. Growing up in India, I was surrounded by the healing power of natural, chemical-free skincare ingredients. Ayurveda was a vital part of my daily routine, offering effective solutions. But when I moved to the US, I found it difficult to find the same clean, natural formulas I had relied on.</p><p>That’s when the idea for Avni Life struck me. If I was struggling to find these solutions, I knew there had to be other women facing similar challenges. I wanted to create a space where they could discover natural, eco-friendly alternatives to traditional skincare products. My goal is to flip the script on beauty and wellness, celebrating the stunning, inherent beauty that exists within all of us.</p><p>Avni Life isn’t just a brand; it’s a message of hope. I offer products rooted in nature and Ayurveda to transform your skincare journey and support you along the way. So, let’s embark on this inspiring journey together and celebrate your unique path to rediscovering the radiant, natural you.</p>"
